<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١١٢٤٠ -<span class="c5"> حَدِيثُ:</span> <span class="c1">" الْبَيِّعَانِ بِالْخِيَارِ "</span>.<span class="c5"> فِي تَرْجَمَةِ:</span> عَبْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ دِينَارٍ، عَنِ ابْنِ عُمَرَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>